        <div class="col-md-6 forFading">
            <img src="/images/home/service-listing.jpg" class="rounded img-fluid" alt="...">
            <strong>Service Listings</strong>
            <p>
                Browse through a diverse selection of service providers, each vetted for their expertise and reliability. With detailed profiles, you can make informed decisions that suit your needs.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 forFading">
            <img src="/images/home/booking.jpg" class="rounded img-fluid" alt="...">
            <strong>Easy Bookings</strong>
            <p>
                We make it simple to book services directly, saving you time and hassle. Find the right service provider, check their availability, and secure your appointment in just a few clicks.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-md-6 forFading">
            <img src="/images/home/communication.jpg" class="rounded img-fluid" alt="...">
            <strong>Direct Communication</strong>
            <p>
                Need to ask questions or discuss specific details? Our messaging feature lets you communicate directly with service providers, ensuring a smooth and personalized experience.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 forFading">
            <img src="/images/home/reviews.jpg" class="rounded img-fluid" alt="...">
            <strong>Customer Reviews</strong> 
            <p>
                Share your experiences and read reviews from others to help you make the best choice. Service Finder is a community where trust and quality service are paramount.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>